import React from 'react'
import { container, Row, Col } from 'react-bootstrap'
const Home = () => {
    return (
        <React.Fragment>
            <Container>
                <Row>
                <Col>1 of 2</Col>
                <Col>2 of 2</Col>
                </Row>
                <Row>
                <Col>1 of 3</Col>
                <Col>2 of 3</Col>
                <Col>3 of 3</Col>
                </Row>
            </Container>
        </React.Fragment>
    )
}

export default Home
